OL,7,Foffenders have been deported since
OL,8,FJuly 2024, a 14% increase on the 12
OL,9,Fmonths prior, according to the
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FMahmood's proposed law chamge could
OL,13,Fsave taxpayers an average #54,000 per
OL,14,Fyear, per prison place.
